{"type":null,"faqId":49957,"title":"华为智能手表_如何调节链式表带的长度？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body27088563\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__p3377841165918\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__b23380318171840\">调整链式表带需要特殊的工具，建议您前往当地专业机构（例如华为手表的零售商店或者传统手表店）进行调整，以避免自己手动调整时误操作而损坏手表表带。</strong></p><ol id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__ol60057706\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__li42470482\">准备好拆卸机座，将表带轻轻摆放在机座上，特别注意表带有箭头的方向对应机座拆卸顶针。<p class=\"litext\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__p46690023\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4e6_6hphx.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p></li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__li23795519\">慢慢旋转顶针，将顶针旋入带身侧孔内。<p class=\"litext\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__p12833084\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4e7_1qmxd.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p></li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__li32846918\">旋转顶针直到钢针从另一侧伸出，用手将钢针拉出即可。<p class=\"litext\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__p27186813\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4e8_zr3r7.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p></li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__li54648243\">取出钢针，带身已脱开；可按照此方法拆出其它带粒，调至适合自己手腕。<div class=\"note\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__note22072140\"><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4e9_20r8f.gif\"><span class=\"notetitle\"> 说明： </span><div class=\"notebody\"><p class=\"text\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__p64431533\">带身脱落后，请避免中珠孔内的通管掉出。如发现掉出请按照箭头方向放入即可。<span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4ea_rjq7i.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4eb_pbpof.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p></div></div></li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__li61491827\">将表带重新连接起来，请注意钢针是从箭头反方向穿入孔内。<span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4ec_pl8pi.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__li14782087\">由于钢针与通管有摩擦，无法轻易的将钢针穿入带身，可以利用机座的平面将钢针用力压入带身内。<p class=\"litext\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__p65929926\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4ed_rqjwl.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p></li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__li38723810\">将连接好的表带再次放入机座， 旋转顶针使它对准连接钢针后轻轻旋转，当听到“啪”声后方可完成（钢针凹槽已进入通管凸槽）。<p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329099__p12969978\"><span><img src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/7c4ee_bpekg.png\" title=\"点击放大\" class=\"imgResize\"></span></p></li></ol></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":207,"faqType":"外观结构&配件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329099","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Appearance-Shell-Accessories","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448627734000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":38,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"链式表带，不锈钢表带，通管，脱落","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}